Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:07.32,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\be2\shad0\bord2\frz1.5\fs34\t(\fs32)\move(364.797,35,364.797,54,24,7323)\c&&HC9D4D7&}Warning
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.52,0:00:03.10,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Dear Viewers Sitting in Front of the Television,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.10,0:00:05.27,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,the guys that appear in this anime are delinquents.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.27,0:00:07.98,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,So, please do not imitate what you see in this anime.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.57,0:00:09.98,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\shad0\fnAveria Sans\b1\i0\bord0\blur0.3\fad(450,0)\c&HDADADA&\fs33\pos(362.532,49)}Do not imitate{\i1\fs40}!{\i0\fs33} Or this will happen{\i1\fs40}!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.83,0:00:23.79,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(250,350)\an8}僕が泣いているのは とても悔しいからです
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.83,0:00:23.79,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(250,350)\an8}Boku ga naite iru no wa totemo kuyashii kara desu
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.83,0:00:23.79,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(250,350)}The reason I am crying is\Nbecause I am very frustrated
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.79,0:00:29.25,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}人の尊さやさしさ 踏みにじられそうで
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.79,0:00:29.25,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}Hito no toutosa yasashisa fuminijiraresou de
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.79,0:00:29.25,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)}I feel as though the nobility and\Nkindness of man is being trampled
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.25,0:00:31.88,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}力を示す者達は
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.25,0:00:31.88,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}Chikara o shimesu mono tachi
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.88,0:00:34.51,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}しなやかさを失って
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.88,0:00:34.51,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}Shinayakasa o ushinatte
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.25,0:00:34.51,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)}Those who show their strength lose their grace
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.51,0:00:40.06,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}ウソまみれドロまみれ じれったい風景でしょう
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.51,0:00:40.06,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}Uso-mamire doro-mamire jirettai fuukei desho
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.51,0:00:40.06,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)}Covered in dirt and lies, isn't it a vexing sight?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.06,0:00:45.35,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}より強くしたたかに タフな生き方をしましょう
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.06,0:00:45.35,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}Yori tsuyoku shitataka ni tafu na ikikata o shimashou
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.06,0:00:45.35,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)}Let's live more strongly, fiercely, and tougher
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.35,0:00:47.61,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}まっすぐ歩きましょう
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.35,0:00:47.61,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}Massugu arukimasho
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.35,0:00:47.61,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)}Let's walk straight
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.61,0:00:51.99,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}風は向かい風
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.61,0:00:51.99,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}Kaze wa mukai kaze
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.61,0:00:51.99,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)}The wind is against us
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.49,0:00:58.83,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}どけ どけ どけ 後ろめたい奴はどけ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.49,0:00:58.83,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}Doke doke doke ushirometai yatsu wa doke
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.49,0:00:58.83,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)}Move, move, move, those with\Na guilty conscience, move aside
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.83,0:01:03.45,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}有象無象の町に 灯りをともせ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.83,0:01:03.45,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}Uzoumuzou no machi ni akari o tomose
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.83,0:01:03.45,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)}Light up the town of riffraff
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.96,0:01:08.92,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}どけ そこ どけ 真実のお通りだ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.96,0:01:08.92,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}Doke soko doke shinjitsu no otouri da
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.96,0:01:08.92,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)}Move, make way, truth is coming through
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.34,0:01:11.84,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}正義の時代がくるさ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.34,0:01:11.84,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}Seigi no jidai ga kuru sa
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.34,0:01:11.84,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)}The era of justice will come
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.84,0:01:14.55,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}希望の歌もあるさ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.84,0:01:14.55,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}Kibou no uta mo aru sa
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.84,0:01:14.55,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)}There are songs of hope too
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.55,0:01:20.39,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(350,500)\an8}僕の命この世に 捧げてしまっていいさ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.55,0:01:20.39,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(350,500)\an8}Boku no inochi kono yo ni sasagete-shimatte ii sa
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.55,0:01:20.39,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(350,500)}I would happily sacrifice my life for this world
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.90,0:02:17.86,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\be2\fad(480,0)}Cromartie Municipal High School (Co-Ed)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.80,0:02:48.48,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\be2\pos(396.519,390)}Shinjiro Hayashida (16)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.40,0:02:59.36,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,So it goes something like that,\Nbut do you know what song it is?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.36,0:03:00.78,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Well, not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.53,0:03:03.24,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I got it, Hayashida.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.24,0:03:06.91,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,What? Really, Kamiyama?\NWhat's the title of this song?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.91,0:03:11.92,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\be2\pos(354.601,388)}Takashi Kamiyama (16)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.91,0:03:11.92,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Well, unfortunately I don't know the title either,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.54,0:03:14.13,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,but I know that song.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.13,0:03:16.13,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,That's no help then, is it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.13,0:03:19.67,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Then I'll hum it this time.\NSomething may come out.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.97,0:03:22.05,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Are you ready, Maeda? Listen carefully, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.05,0:03:22.84,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,What? Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.84,0:03:25.05,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\be3\pos(368.196,392)}Akira Maeda (16)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.22,0:03:25.05,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.49,0:03:53.04,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Hold on a second. Sorry, but I feel\Nthat it's different from my song.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.04,0:03:54.38,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,What? Different?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.38,0:03:56.09,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,The song I'm talking about goes...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.38,0:04:01.22,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,...like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.22,0:04:04.14,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I see. Sorry about that. My song goes...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.98,0:04:11.89,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,...like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.15,0:04:19.28,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Hold on a second, then what's\Nthe song that I just hummed?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.28,0:04:19.69,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Who cares?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.40,0:04:22.70,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,We won't get anywhere if\Nwe're doing several songs!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.70,0:04:25.53,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Let's take care of Hayashida's song first.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.03,0:04:28.03,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Then I'll try humming it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.12,0:04:34.50,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Somehow I feel it's different\Nfrom the melody earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.50,0:04:38.17,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Why don't you guys go to a CD store\Nor something and sing there?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.17,0:04:39.50,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,The store clerks might know it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.51,0:04:42.22,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Are you stupid?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.22,0:04:45.68,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,It's too embarrassing to sing in a CD store!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.68,0:04:48.72,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,That's right. It's true that we can sing here\Nbecause we know everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.72,0:04:51.39,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I think you guys would be able to sing anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.77,0:04:58.40,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I wish I at least knew the lyrics.\NHumming the melody isn't really...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.40,0:05:01.19,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,You're really stupid, aren't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.19,0:05:03.61,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,If I knew the lyrics,\N I wouldn't be doing things like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.61,0:05:07.28,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,It seems that we can't get\Nany further on our own.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.28,0:05:09.58,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,We don't have any other choice\Nbut to ask others to help us too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.55,0:05:24.80,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,That's enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.63,0:05:29.14,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,A song you unexpectedly heard\Nnever leaves your head,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.14,0:05:31.31,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,but you don't know the title of the song.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.31,0:05:33.35,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,That kind of thing can happen to anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.93,0:05:36.56,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,It's annoying if the song comes\N into your head right before you go to bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.56,0:05:38.65,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that drives me nuts.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.15,0:05:41.65,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Okay, we'll help you too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.65,0:05:44.78,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Thanks. Then I'll hum it this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.59,0:06:11.97,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I've heard of it, but I still\Ncan't remember the title.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.97,0:06:13.39,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,As I thought, it's different somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.39,0:06:15.77,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,It's just on the tip of my tongue, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.77,0:06:20.02,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Damn! I won't feel relieved either,\Nunless I remember the title.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.02,0:06:22.40,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I'll do whatever it takes to remember it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.40,0:06:25.40,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,All right, then! You guys go and ask others too!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.65,0:06:27.07,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Thanks, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.70,0:06:34.16,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,It sounds like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.67,0:06:48.76,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Like that, right? I've heard of it. What was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.77,0:07:00.06,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.06,0:07:02.02,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Yeah... What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.69,0:07:06.23,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.23,0:07:07.99,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,That's not it! We'll kill you, bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.70,0:07:14.53,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.42,0:07:28.38,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\be2\fad(500,0)\pos(319.481,394)\fs26}Yutaka Takenouchi (16)
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.46,0:08:48.75,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,By the way...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.25,0:08:51.80,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Was someone able\N to remember the title of the song?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.80,0:08:54.38,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,No, it's getting more confusing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.38,0:09:02.14,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,We don't know the title, but one thing I can say\Nis that everyone's singing has improved.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.48,0:09:09.15,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Wouldn't it be better if we sang in parts\Nof high tone and low tone?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.15,0:09:11.03,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,No, that's not the point.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.33,0:09:21.29,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Dear Mother,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.83,0:09:24.37,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,We didn't figure out the title of this song after all,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.37,0:09:27.46,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,but I still have this mysterious\Nsense of accomplishment.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.96,0:09:35.34,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,That's it! It's that song!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.34,0:09:39.51,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Mechazawa is humming it,\Nwhich means he knows this song.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.51,0:09:40.35,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Probably.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.56,0:09:43.72,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Mechazawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.02,0:09:48.98,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\be2\pos(353.468,387)}Takashi Kamiyama (16)
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.73,0:09:48.98,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Do you often hum that song?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.19,0:09:52.23,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I like this song.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.77,0:09:56.95,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\be2\pos(370.462,389)}Shinichi Mechazawa (16)
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.87,0:10:09.46,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Do you like this song too, Kamiyama?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.46,0:10:10.38,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Well, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.79,0:10:14.42,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Darn! I just carelessly answered\Nhis question without thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.42,0:10:19.13,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Now I can't ask "what's this song?"\Nanymore, can I?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.27,0:10:33.82,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Even two hours later, we were still going at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.00,0:11:45.01,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\shad0\alpha130\fs24\fnNeon\bord0\c&H4E1728&\blur0.5\pos(346.671,139)}Next\N\N\N\NEpisode
Dialogue: 1,0:11:45.01,0:11:50.02,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\shad0\fs26\blur0.5\fnArial Black\bord3\c&H000000&\3c&HFBFAFC&\pos(203.924,50)}Sakigake!!\NCromartie High School
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.01,0:11:50.02,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\shad0\fs26\blur0.6\fnArial Black\bord3.2\c&H000000&\3c&H3F3F3F&\pos(203.924,50)}Sakigake!!\NCromartie High School
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.01,0:11:50.02,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\shad0\fnArial Black\fs36\bord2.2\blur0.5\pos(572.12,390)}Later
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.25,0:11:37.55,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Dear Mother,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.55,0:11:41.30,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I have to talk about the next episode of\NSakigake!! Cromartie High School.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.30,0:11:45.01,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,But... Let me see... We have another episode.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.01,0:11:50.02,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\fs26\shad1\be1\bord0.7\c&HEAEDED&\pos(202.791,145)}The title of the humming
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.01,0:11:50.02,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\fs26\shad1\be1\bord0.7\c&HEAEDED&\pos(275.297,170)}song:
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.01,0:11:50.02,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\fs26\shad1\be1\bord0.7\pos(244.709,229)\c&HEAEDED&}"Ningen Nante"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.55,0:11:47.10,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Hayashida, what's the next episode about?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.10,0:11:48.77,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Don't ask me!
